Install instructions for AppCSXCAD:
---------------------------------------------

1) Prerequirements:
  AppCSXCAD relies on the QCSXCAD & CSXCAD libraries and its dependencies:
  - CSXCAD, QCSXCAD (http://openEMS.de)

2) Build:
  - change directory to QCSXCAD
  - build:
    qmake PREFIX=<path/to/install/> CSXCAD_ROOT=<path/to/CSXCAD> QCSXCAD_ROOT=<path/to/QCSXCAD> AppCSXCAD.pro
    make
    make install (may require root)

    Note:
      - all path informations may be stored in a localPathes.pri
      - the default "prefix" is /usr/local

